{| class="wikitable"
|-
| Element || Description || Required
|-
| vtn_name || VTN name.
Valid value: Up to 31
characters that can include
alphabets, numbers, and
underscore (except at the
beginning). 
||Yes
|-
|vbr_name || vBridge name.
Valid value: Up to 31
characters that can include
alphabets, numbers, and
underscore (except at the
beginning). 
||Yes
|}


